Package semanticMarkup.know

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICharacterKnowledgeBase
    An ICharacterKnowledgeBase allows the management and lookup of character names for character states
    ICorpus
    An ICorpus allows lookup of word frequencies within the corpus
    IGlossary
    An IGlossary allows to lookup categories of words and vice versa
    IOrganStateKnowledgeBase
    An IOrganStateKnowledgeBase allows the management and lookup of organs and states
    IPOSKnowledgeBase
    An IPOSKnowledgeBase allows the management, lookup, and verification of part of speech of words
